<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/resources/{resourceKey}/content"}
  context={"endpoint"}
></MethodEndpoint>

Returns the content of a deployed resource.
:::info
Currently, this endpoint only supports RPA resources.
:::
